									<children>
										<node id="data" key="key">
											<attribute id="key" type="FixedString" value="CinematicNodeContext" />
											<attribute id="val" type="LSString" value="The player enters a gore-soaked alcove and approaches the displacer.There's various severed heads on display - people and monsters. A pile of eviscerated corpses forms a throne-chaise.&#xD;&#xA;There's suddenly a loud click from above (implied to be the orthon racking/loading its crossbow). The player looks up.&#xD;&#xA;The orthon looms on a gallery/crumpling floor overlooking the alcove. It aims a crossbow at the player. Flanking it are several merregons." />
										</node>
									</children>
								</node>
							</children>
						</node>
